channel.title: Eclipse 639 webclient stuck at 1%?
channel.description:
I've posted MULTIPLE topics about this, and spent hours upon hours on this problem. SOMEONE GIVE ME A STRAIGHT ANSWER.
it stays at "checking for updates" 1%. Yes, the client is set to go to my no-ip address, and yes, I did jar it correctly. someone give me a straight answer, no go to this section or anything like that. I've been going in circles too many times.
I should also point out that the client doesnt have a signlink.java, and I have no idea where to get one. if you would like to see my problem, go to rspsinfo.blogspot.com
